{"tid":1369103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［法科］一齊念咒咒何君堯","createTime":"2019-07-26T15:30:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T17:04:17.000Z","uid":54046,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8c716bb17f7be1e2f830f624897d5378d3fbb440","tid":1369103,"uid":54046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:30:11.000Z","msg":"正一天傷，元首從良。天師有旨，速捉禍殃。徧通九地，殺鬼擒傷。善者降福，惡者降殃。惡人憎我，盡死報傷。吾令使汝，大逞猖狂。急急如律令。<br />\n<br />\n空中寫「惡人何君堯生於1962年6月4日」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n普通人念都有用，希望可以多d人念<br />\n唔信唔好理我就可以，信既就念多d"},{"pid":"f1c517d9712d0739dff625d5bd77fedd12eccb7d","tid":1369103,"uid":54046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:36:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"954feccf71b1e2b6e7097ed612816d30c18f18b1","tid":1369103,"uid":54046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:40:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c28e334efe92a0424bd53f044657865fd92936","tid":1369103,"uid":54046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:40:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98fe65a842efe80ab79fa22e7aae06abe3b9549","tid":1369103,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:42:23.000Z","msg":"河妖東<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096ed43d3d2dac108ddac37ef8363734048f8693","tid":1369103,"uid":54046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}